Adapty privacy policy
This Privacy Policy explains what personal data is collected when you visit or use the website located at:
https://adapty.io/
(the “Website”), the services and products provided through it (together with the Website, the “Service”), how such personal data will be processed.
1. Personal data controller
2. Categories of personal data we collect
3. For what purposes we process your personal data
4. Under what legal bases we process your personal data
5. With whom we share your personal data
6. How you can exercise your privacy rights
7. Age limitation
8. International data transfers
9. Data Privacy Frameworks
10. Changes to this privacy policy
